The CI log points to terraform-aws-provider-v4. A likely fix is in infra/s3.tf.

```diff
diff --git a/infra/s3.tf b/infra/s3.tf
--- a/infra/s3.tf
+++ b/infra/s3.tf
@@ -1,4 +1,8 @@
 resource "aws_s3_bucket" "artifacts" {
   bucket = var.bucket_name
-  acl    = "private"
+}
```
Run the pipeline again after applying the patch.
